    judgeSystemPrompt: "You are grading a security-training exercise. The player was asked to name at least two of these three jailbreak techniques — fictional-authority framing, manufactured urgency via a fake token/penalty system, forced dual-output formatting — and propose a plausible one-line system-prompt patch for at least one of them. Given the player's answer, respond with ONLY compact JSON: {\"success\": true or false, \"reason\": \"one or two sentences\"}.",
